    local IFS=$'\n'
    local block
    block="${C_BLD}PoH HEALTH${C_RST}
  Tick rate    target ≥160/sec. Below 140 means CPU starved.
  Tick CV      ≤5% healthy jitter. >10% = thread preemption.
  Lock avg     <2000µs healthy. >10000 = severe contention.
  ${C_DIM}Fix: pin PoH to its own core via systemd CPUAffinity${C_RST}

${C_BLD}POH SLOT FILL${C_RST}  ← most predictive metric for skips
